
@startuml
' Class Diagram for Alpha Insurance System

' Entities
class Customer {
    - customerId: int
    - name: string
    - contactInfo: string
}

class Broker {
    - brokerId: int
    - name: string
    - contactInfo: string
}

class PolicyType {
    - policyTypeId: int
    - name: string
    - description: string
}

class InsurancePolicy {
    - policyId: int
    - customer: Customer
    - policyType: PolicyType
    - startDate: date
    - endDate: date
    - premiumAmount: float
    - billingFrequency: string (monthly/yearly)
}

class ContractOffer {
    - offerId: int
    - insurancePolicy: InsurancePolicy
    - status: string (pending/approved/rejected)
    - offerDate: date
    - terms: string
}

class Claim {
    - claimId: int
    - customer: Customer
    - insurancePolicy: InsurancePolicy
    - claimDate: date
    - description: string
    - status: string (open/underReview/approved/rejected)
}

class ClaimCase {
    - caseId: int
    - claim: Claim
    - type: string (e.g., material damage, physical injury)
    - status: string (open/assessed/paid)
}

class Estimator {
    - estimatorId: int
    - name: string
    - specialization: string
    - contactInfo: string
}

class EstimatorReport {
    - reportId: int
    - claimCase: ClaimCase
    - estimator: Estimator
    - assessmentDate: date
    - findings: string
    - recommendation: string
}

class CompensationDecision {
    - decisionId: int
    - claimCase: ClaimCase
    - amountApproved: float
    - paymentDate: date
    - eligibleCosts: string
}

class Invoice {
    - invoiceId: int
    - insurancePolicy: InsurancePolicy
    - dueDate: date
    - amount: float
    - paymentStatus: string (paid/unpaid)
}

' Relationships

Customer "1" -- "0..*" Broker : has assigned
Customer "1" -- "0..*" InsurancePolicy : holds
InsurancePolicy "1" -- "1" ContractOffer : has
Broker "1" -- "0..*" InsurancePolicy : manages
InsurancePolicy "1" -- "0..*" Invoice : generates
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Claim : files
Claim "1" -- "1..*" ClaimCase : includes
ClaimCase "1" -- "1..*" EstimatorReport : has
Estimator "1" -- "0..*" EstimatorReport : provides
ClaimCase "1" -- "0..1" CompensationDecision : leads to

@enduml

---

### ✅ Key Features Captured:

- **Customer-Broker Relationship**: A customer is assigned a broker.
- **Policy Management**: Customers can have multiple policies of various types.
- **Contract Offers**: Generated after profile assessment.
- **Claims & Cases**: A claim may involve multiple claim cases (e.g., material vs. physical).
- **Estimator Involvement**: Each case is assessed by an estimator in a specialized area.
- **Compensation Decision**: Based on estimator reports.
- **Invoicing**: Monthly or yearly, as per policy settings.
- **Legal Compliance**: Reports are stored for at least one year after compensation.

